  <x:String x:Key="Text.Configure.CommitMessageTemplate.BuiltinVars" xml:space="preserve">—Е–Х–Ј—ЕвХЧвХС—Е–Я–У—Ж–•вХХ:

  ${branch_name} —З–Ђ–Њ—Е–Щ–Э—Е–Ш–Ц—Ж–§–њ—Е–†–Э—З–ЄвЦТ
